(61, 2, 'career', '{\"_token\":\"MAP8RKuRRHhI2M8Tb15RAYHPhnHrVI34DkUXO5uk\",\"name\":\"Teaching Assistant\",\"slug\":\"senior-real-estate-consultant\",\"slug_id\":\"76\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Career\\\\Models\\\\Career\",\"location\":\"Ho Chi Minh, Viet Nam\",\"salary\":\"Negotiable\",\"description\":\"<p><strong><span style=\\\"color:#16a085;\\\">Job Overview: <\\/span><\\/strong><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Teaching Assistant supports the teachers in enabling the pupils to gain independence and participate fully in the curriculum and general life of the school. Responsibilities and Duties:<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&bull; Support students during lessons as directed by the class teacher.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&bull; Supervise and teach individual, pairs or groups of children as required by the class teacher or line manager.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&bull; Be aware, in advance of the teacher&rsquo;s weekly planning.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&bull; Contribute to the planning of lessons.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&bull; Assist in lesson preparation.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&bull; Provide feedback to the teacher regarding the performance of students the TA has been assigned to work with during a lesson.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&bull; Supervise students in communal areas to ensure a high standard of behaviour is maintained.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&bull; Assist with the supervision of snack times and carry out allocated playground, lunchtime and afterschool duties as agreed.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&bull; Organise - and have responsibility for - two Curriculum Option Lessons each term.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&bull; Assist the teacher in displaying and removing students&rsquo; work.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&bull; Reward and sanction children in accordance with the school&rsquo;s &lsquo;Positive Behaviour&rsquo; policy to ensure the school&rsquo;s high standards of behaviour and discipline are maintained.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&bull; Collect notices, reply slips etc. Collate and send to office when required.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p