(213, 2, 'page', '{\"_token\":\"CVneRslocLUfNiRMQMfTJ7Z7ZaALO4eEhI2jrb9A\",\"name\":\"Student Council\",\"slug\":\"student-council\",\"slug_id\":\"0\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"description\":\"The Student Council is active in bringing ideas and suggestions to the school\'s leadership for consideration, and in so doing, they are increasingly helping to shape school direction and strategic planning. they are taking a role in shaping school direction and strategic planning.\",\"content\":\"<h1 style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-size:24px;\\\">Student Council<\\/span><\\/h1>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" height=\\\"333\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/batdongsan.local\\/storage\\/primaryyears\\/hinhnen3.jpg\\\" width=\\\"500\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>The Student Council is active in bringing ideas and suggestions to the school&#39;s leadership for consideration, and in so doing, they are increasingly helping to shape school direction and strategic planning. they are taking a role in shaping school direction and strategic planning.&nbsp; &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>One of the crucial elements of an International Baccalaureate education is the need to provide students with real-world and authentic issues and problems to address. The Student Council offers our young ambassadors a chance to deal with real problems to find genuine solutions. It is always a pleasure to see how the critical thinking skills they have learned in the classroom can be translated into solving school-related issues. &nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Our Student Council has had significant input into our school Vision Narrative, has promoted healthy food options in the canteen, and led countless events.<\\/p>\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"gallery\":\"[{\\\"img\\\":\\\"primaryyears\\/betraimamnon.jpg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"primaryyears\\/library.jpg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"primaryyears\\/hinhnen3.jpg\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"},{\\\"img\\\":\\\"primaryyears\\/img-menublock.png\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"\\\"}]\",\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"en_US\",\"ref_from\":null,\"status\":\"published\",\"template\":\"default\",\"image\":\"primaryyears\\/football.jpg\"}', 'created', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/79.0.3945.130 Safari/537.36', '127.0.0.1', 2, 13, 'Student Council', 'info', '2020-02-09 10:38:04', '2020-02-09 10:38:04'),
