(367, 3, 'page', '{\"_token\":\"xfbikW6Je58DGdldu9DGahhEpIUNqmVLuuRhiveJ\",\"name\":\"Brendan Hearne\",\"slug\":\"brendan-hearne\",\"slug_id\":\"0\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"description\":\"Director of Learning and Development\",\"content\":\"<h1 style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Our Teachers<\\/span><\\/h1>\\r\\n\\r\\n<article itemscope=\\\"\\\" itemtype=\\\"http:\\/\\/schema.org\\/Article\\\">\\r\\n<header>\\r\\n<h2 itemprop=\\\"name\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Brendan Hearne<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" height=\\\"400\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/sgstar.edu.vn\\/storage\\/teacher\\/brendan-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"400\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Director of Learning and Development<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>First Class BA (Hons) in Primary Education with Qualified Teacher Status, St. Martin&#39;s College, Ambleside.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Brendan originates from the UK and first joined Saigon Star International School in August 2013 .<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>After spent several years as Deputy Head and&nbsp;Headteacher, Brendan led Saigon Star to become the first IPC-accredited school in Vietnam. During this time he became a regional trainer for the International Primary Curriculum (IPC ) and is also a member of Fieldwork Education&#39;s IPC Accreditation Team.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>He now dedicates his time to school improvement and is also currently working towards a Masters in Education with the University of Bath.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/header>\\r\\n<\\/article>\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"en_US\",\"ref_from\":null,\"status\":\"published\",\"template\":\"default\",\"image\":\"teacher\\/brendan-1.jpg\"}', 'created', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Wi