stand who they are and their place in the world <a href=\\\"{{URL::to(\'\\/\')}}\\/storage\\/File\\/Understand-your-place-in-the-world.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\"> <\\/a><button class=\\\"btn\\\">Download File<\\/button><a href=\\\"{{URL::to(\'\\/\')}}\\/storage\\/File\\/Understand-your-place-in-the-world.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\"> <\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>- How to talk about learning with your child <a href=\\\"{{URL::to(\'\\/\')}}\\/storage\\/File\\/Show-me-Tell-me-Talk-to-me.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\"> <\\/a><button class=\\\"btn\\\">Download File<\\/button><a href=\\\"{{URL::to(\'\\/\')}}\\/storage\\/File\\/Show-me-Tell-me-Talk-to-me.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\"> <\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>- Ten things to say to your child that will make all the difference <a href=\\\"{{URL::to(\'\\/\')}}\\/storage\\/File\\/The-ten-things-you-can-say-to-your-child.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\"> <\\/a><button class=\\\"btn\\\">Download File<\\/button><a href=\\\"{{URL::to(\'\\/\')}}\\/storage\\/File\\/The-ten-things-you-can-say-to-your-child.pdf\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\"> <\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h1 class=\\\"titlepg\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">The Personal Goals:<\\/span><\\/h1>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Below are age-appropriate challenges that your child can do at home. Children do not have to do all of the tasks but we encourage them to try and complete one for each of the nine personal goals over the course of their milepost (two years). Taking photos and videos of children&rsquo;s progress is a great way for parents to get involved, and also helpful for teachers to decide if children have challenged themselves sufficiently in order to receive a badge for their school bag. In some cases, teachers may decide that the task is &#39;not finished yet&#39; and encourage learners to spend a little more time on it.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h1><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Home-Learning Menus:<\\/span><\\/h1>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>- Early Years <a href=\\\"{{URL::to(\'\\/\')}}\\/sto