(385, 3, 'page', '{\"_token\":\"xfbikW6Je58DGdldu9DGahhEpIUNqmVLuuRhiveJ\",\"name\":\"Patricia Barnwell\",\"slug\":\"patricia-barnwell\",\"slug_id\":\"0\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"description\":\"Bachelor of Education (with History), St. Patrick\\u2019s College, Dublin\",\"content\":\"<h1 style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Our Teachers<\\/span><\\/h1>\\r\\n\\r\\n<article itemscope=\\\"\\\" itemtype=\\\"http:\\/\\/schema.org\\/Article\\\">\\r\\n<header>\\r\\n<h2 itemprop=\\\"name\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Neil Jones<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" height=\\\"400\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/sgstar.edu.vn\\/storage\\/teacher\\/patricia.jpg\\\" width=\\\"400\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/header>\\r\\n<\\/article>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Learning Support Teacher<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Bachelor of Education (with History), St. Patrick&rsquo;s College, Dublin<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Trisha graduated in 2013 and taught in Irish primary schools until 2018. As well as being a Class Teacher, Trisha also worked as a Learning Support teacher for two of these years.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>In 2018, Trisha joined Saigon Star International School as a Year 2 Class Teacher. This Year, Trisha is excited to move into the role of Learning Support Teacher, and will endeavor to provide the care and skills needed to create a positive and inclusive learning environment for all children.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>In her free time Trisha loves to travel, read and be active. She is enjoying living in Vietnam and appreciates the endless opportunities to explore new cultures and meet new people.&nbsp;<\\/p>\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"en_US\",\"ref_from\":null,\"status\":\"published\",\"template\":\"default\",\"image\":\"teacher\\/patricia.jpg\"}', 'created', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/79.0.3945.130 Safari/537.36', '14.241.249.67', 3, 36, 'Patricia Barnwell', 'info', '2020-02-21 02:51:41', '2020-02-21 02:51:41'),
(386, 3, 'page', '{\"_token\":\"xfbikW6Je58DGdldu9DGahhEpIUNqmVLuuRhiveJ\",\"name\":\"Edward Kellett\",\"slug\":\"edward-kellett\",\"slug_id\":\"0\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"description\":\"Year 5 Class Teacher\\r\\nPost Graduate in Education, University College Dublin (NUI)\\r\\nMSc. in Electronic Commerce, Dublin City University, Ireland\",\"content\":\"<h1 style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Our Teachers<\\/span><\\/h1>\\r\\n\\r\\n<article itemscope=\\\"\\\" itemtype=\\\"http:\\/\\/schema.org\\/Article\\\">\\r\\n<header>\\r\\n<h2 itemprop=\\\"name\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Edward Kellett<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" height=\\\"400\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/sgstar.edu.vn\\/storage\\/teacher\\/ed.jpg\\\" width=\\\"400\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Year 3&nbsp;Class Teacher<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Bachelor of Education Degree, with International Perspective, Mary Immaculate College, Limerick, Ireland.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Conor comes to us from Ireland. He graduated from University in 2016 and since then has been teaching full-time in Ireland and in Vietnam.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>While in University, Conor studied Education in an International Perspective and this sparked his love and passion for education in an international setting. He enjoys learning about new cultures and traditions and sharing these experiences with his students. Conor would describe himself as creative, innovative and passionate about teaching. Conor aims to make learning fun, active and engaging for all his students, and enjoys nurturing each child to reach their potential.&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Conor loves living in Vietnam and enjoys the culture, traditions and food. In his spare time Conor enjoys keeping fit, travelling and motorbike trips.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/header>\\r\\n<\\/article>\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"en_US\",\"ref_from\":null,\"status\":\"published\",\"template\":\"default\",\"image\":\"teacher\\/ed.jpg\"}', 'created', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/79.0.3945.130 Safari/537.36', '14.241.249.67', 3, 37, 'Edward Kellett', 'info', '2020-02-21 02:53:47', '2020-02-21 02:53:47'),
(387, 3, 'page', '{\"_token\":\"xfbikW6Je58DGdldu9DGahhEpIUNqmVLuuRhiveJ\",\"name\":\"Carlos Marques\",\"slug\":\"carlos-marques\",\"slug_id\":\"0\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"description\":\"Bachelor in Education, majoring in Physical Education, Leiria Institute, Portugal\",\"content\":\"<h1 style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Our Teachers<\\/span><\\/h1>\\r\\n\\r\\n<article itemscope=\\\"\\\" itemtype=\\\"http:\\/\\/schema.org\\/Article\\\">\\r\\n<header>\\r\\n<h2 itemprop=\\\"name\\\" style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Carlos Marques<\\/span><\\/h2>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align:center\\\"><img alt=\\\"\\\" height=\\\"400\\\" src=\\\"http:\\/\\/sgstar.edu.vn\\/storage\\/teacher\\/carlos-1.jpg\\\" width=\\\"400\\\" \\/><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>&nbsp;<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Physical Education Specialist Teacher<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Bachelor in Education, majoring in Physical Education, Leiria Institute, Portugal<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Carlos was born and raised in Portugal. He received his PE teaching degree from one of the top education institutes in his country. He taught in several schools around the western region of Portugal for 11 years and then moved inland to a completely different region for a couple of years. From there he decided to follow the spirit of his ancestors and departed East to discover the true Asian culture. Since then he has taught in China and Timor Leste before settling in Malaysia for 7 years, which represented an enriching experience. He is now looking forward to a brand new experience in Vietnam, with the most enthusiastic spirit and motivation. Besides being an experienced teacher over all year groups, from Pre-school through to Year 12, he is a certified Basketball coach, Swimming instructor, Life Guard and Basketball referee. His sports background also includes Hockey, Badminton, Athletics, Volleyball, Football and Roller Skating. Other than his passion for sports, Carlos is an enthusiastic researcher in diverse areas such as Geography, Music, History and Cinema. He also plays drums and guitar during his free time.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/header>\\r\\n<\\/article>\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"en_US\",\"ref_from\":null,\"status\":\"published\",\"template\":\"default\",\"image\":\"teacher\\/carlos-1.jpg\"}', 'created', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/79.0.3945.130 Safari/537.36', '14.241.249.67', 3, 38, 'Carlos Marques', 'info', '2020-02-21 02:56:20', '2020-02-21 02:56:20'),
