>Formal offer and contracting<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>N.B. All positions of employment are dependent on comprehensive criminal and professional background checks. In order to receive a valid work permit and temporary residence card, applicants will be required to submit copies of their degree and teaching credentials for Vietnamese officials to check that you meet the minimum criteria.<\\/p>\",\"is_featured\":\"0\",\"gallery\":null,\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"en_US\",\"ref_from\":null,\"status\":\"published\",\"template\":\"default\",\"image\":null}', 'updated', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/79.0.3945.130 Safari/537.36', '14.241.249.67', 3, 23, 'Recruitment/Vacancies', 'primary', '2020-02-21 05:43:32', '2020-02-21 05:43:32'),
