(474, 3, 'page', '{\"_token\":\"q0qMMSHHUNttZMXqYdUB5ceWeUlAI6JQk7ermcTM\",\"name\":\"Admissions\",\"slug\":\"admissions\",\"slug_id\":\"80\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Page\\\\Models\\\\Page\",\"description\":\"adm\",\"content\":\"<h1 class=\\\"titlepg\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\">Admissions Process<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/h1>\\r\\n\\r\\n<div class=\\\"contentpg\\\">\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Admission is granted to a student when it has been determined that the School has an appropriate programme and resources to meet that individual&rsquo;s learning needs. Applications for both immediate and future entry are considered at any time throughout the year.&nbsp;<\\/span> <span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">The birth date cut-off for placement in a particular grade is 31st August in the academic year (commencing in August) of admission. The child must have turned the appropriate age on or prior to 31st August for the grade in question.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\"><strong>Visit Us<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">We recommend that all families visit our campus to find out whether our friendly school community represents a good fit fot you child.&nbsp;<\\/span> <span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Our school office is open and available to assist you with inquiries, school tours and enrolments Monday to Friday, from 07:30 to 16:30 throughout the year, including during school holidays.<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3><span style=\\\"color:#2980b9;\\\"><strong>How to Apply<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">Please <a href=\\\"#\\\"><span style=\\\"color: #ff6600;\\\"><u>complete the online inquiry form and then application form<\\/u><\\/span><\\/a><\\/span><span style=\\\"font-weight: 400;\\\">. The online application portal will prompt you to submit the following supporting documents:<\\/span><\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p s