(598, 3, 'career', '{\"_token\":\"s21WhsLOrmhjUy9TSGX7L16hjTR5oLiGSN6pewAw\",\"name\":\"Teacher Vacancies\",\"slug\":\"teacher-vacancies\",\"slug_id\":\"0\",\"model\":\"Botble\\\\Career\\\\Models\\\\Career\",\"location\":\"Ho Chi Minh, Viet Nam\",\"salary\":\"Negotiable\",\"description\":\"<h1 style=\\\"text-align: center;\\\"><span style=\\\"color:#16a085;\\\">Recruitment<\\/span><\\/h1>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>As a growing school, we are always looking to hear from high-quality teachers. If you feel you would be a good addition to the Saigon Star family, please send an up-to-date CV, covering letter and recent photograph to the Headteacher, Mr. James Quantrill, email:&nbsp;james@sgstar.edu.vn<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p>Applicants must hold Qualified Teacher Status (QTS) and have a minimum of three years teaching experience.<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3 style=\\\"margin-left: 320px;\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"color:#16a085;\\\">Teacher Vacancies<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"margin-left: 280px;\\\">* Vietnamese Language Teacher<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"margin-left: 280px;\\\">* Middle Years Maths, History and Art Teacher (Maternity Cover):<br \\/>\\r\\nStart Date: 15th March 2020<br \\/>\\r\\nEnd Date: 3rd July 2020<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"margin-left: 280px;\\\">* Part-Time Mandarin Language Teacher (Monday - Wednesday):<br \\/>\\r\\nStart Date: Monday 9th December 2019<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<h3 style=\\\"margin-left: 320px;\\\"><strong><span style=\\\"color:#16a085;\\\">Other Vacancies<\\/span><\\/strong><\\/h3>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"margin-left: 280px;\\\">Learning + Teaching Assistant<\\/p>\\r\\n\\r\\n<p style=\\\"margin-left: 280px;\\\">Start Date: ASAP Contract Type: Full-time:<\\/p>\",\"seo_meta\":{\"seo_title\":null,\"seo_description\":null},\"submit\":\"save\",\"language\":\"en_US\",\"ref_from\":null,\"status\":\"published\"}', 'created', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/80.0.3987.122 Safari/537.