(12, 'Bulletin', 0, 'At Saigon Star, we believe it is essential for parents to know and understand as much as possible about what we do. At the same time, we are continuously developing our provision, therefore, this bulletin aims to keep parents up-to-date with school improvements.', 'published', 3, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', NULL, 0, 0, 0, '2020-03-10 22:29:11', '2020-03-17 03:32:03'),
(13, 'Early Years', 12, 'The IEYC is an exciting theme based curriculum which focuses on play based learning and\r\nholistic enquiry, for 2 to 5 year olds. It also includes personal learning goals as well as social\r\nand emotional development. There are 18 fascinating themes across the units, with learning\r\ngoals appropriate to different ages and stages of development.', 'published', 3, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', NULL, 0, 0, 0, '2020-03-15 21:49:53', '2020-03-16 20:42:17'),
(14, 'Primary', 12, 'The IPC is especially designed for ages 5 to 11 and has as many as 130 thematic units of work.\r\nEach theme is specifically designed to motivate and enthuse young learners. The units of\r\nlearning are cross curricula, enabling young minds to see how aspects of learning integrate\r\ntogether and learning goals cover personal development and social and international goals.', 'published', 3, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', NULL, 0, 0, 0, '2020-03-15 21:51:08', '2020-03-16 20:42:32'),
(15, 'Middle Years', 12, 'The IMYC is especially designed for 11 to 14 year olds and is a challenging, internationally\r\nminded and concept-focused curriculum. It also offers the development of a hardworking, ethical\r\nand humane individual through personal learning goals. The IMYC develops knowledge, skills\r\nand understanding, helping students appreciate the interconnections between subjects.', 'published', 3, 'Botble\\ACL\\Models\\User', NULL, 0, 0, 0, '2020-03-15 21:52:19', '2020-03-16 20:43:07');
